@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_icyrvq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v2 + 0.73 / v2 + 0.97)))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = wp.exp((v0 / wp.abs(v2 + 0.27)))
    v2 = (tmp * 0.12)
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.87)) / 0.50)
    tmp = v2
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v2 + 0.20) * (v0 + 0.87 - tmp + 0.51)))
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
